Source:  https://github.com/facebookresearch/MHR
Paper:   https://arxiv.org/abs/2511.15586

MHR provides:
  - Identity parameterization (45 shape parameters)
  - Pose parameterization (204 model parameters)
  - Facial expression parameterization (72 expression parameters)
  - Multiple levels of detail and non-linear pose correctives

