--- Files incorporated from MHR ---

The TorchScript model asset `mhr_model.pt` and its associated metadata are
downloaded at install time from the MHR v1.0.0 release:

    https://github.com/facebookresearch/MHR/releases/download/v1.0.0/assets.zip

The MHR mesh topology (18,439 vertices, 36,874 triangles) is the basis for
the blend-shape authoring workflow used by this project's custom nodes.
Derivative works (custom blend shapes, per-object vertex partitions) are
copyright their respective authors and are licensed under Apache 2.0 for
consistency with MHR.
